{"tid":1811982,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【RTHK確認戰果】黑警：義士向上水狗屋擲汽油彈　別無選擇以催淚彈驅散","createTime":"2020-01-05T07:36:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-05T08:12:16.000Z","uid":79563,"like":22,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"e53c1575622f87cf6e0a7eb1ae6055e5eb98c7d0","tid":1811982,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T07:36:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/540/https://na.cx/i/4vOcb8f.jpg\" /><br />\n<br />\n黑警表示，有義士在上水狗屋投擲汽油彈，黑警在別無選擇的情況下，用催淚煙驅散。<br />\n<br />\n黑警在社交平台的直播畫面，未有顯示上水狗屋及事發經過，而身處上水巡撫街及新康街交界的黑警公共關係科督察鄒昊亨表示，在下午2時40分左右，有義士在上水狗屋投擲一枚汽油彈。黑警在別無選擇的情況下，一定要用最低所需武力包括催淚煙，驅散暴徒的行為。<br />\n<br />\n鄒昊亨表示，黑警強烈讉責任何人向狗屋投擲汽油彈及縱火的行為，同時呼籲任何人，不要騎劫市民和平表達意見的自由及權利；重申黑警尊重市民和平表達意見的自由及權利，會繼續在現場維持公眾安全及公共秩序。"},{"pid":"0137b3e193ec5a8c84347004bb7218af79335c8e","tid":1811982,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T07:36:51.000Z","msg":"SOURCE:<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1501115-20200105.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1501115-20200105.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=x%2FFuRRgY0RqQB1T9iHKuLQwUaSA5OUQt3qQG7WIDhAk%3D&h=e9193625\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1501115-20200105.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=2a5fb5e4\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1501115-20200105.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"e313c980ad1e7f54b0cbde097e70ded22a33a348","tid":1811982,"uid":78769,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T07:38:32.000Z","msg":"ho ball, 示範聲東擊西"},{"pid":"30cfff1997fa48b1cb51c0a971460bc214a1b7f3","tid":1811982,"uid":13541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T07:39:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e18d087f2d9524be49f833a648baf530640163de","tid":1811982,"uid":335708,"like":1,"